lead_paragraph: A mysterious renegade named Brayker is forced to defend a motley crew of boarding-house residents from an army of insatiable demons. Leading the forces of darkness is the Collector, a charismatic soul-taker who is determined to regain possession of an ancient talisman from Brayker.
